summary:
My name is Roy Ahmed from Egystone for granite & natural stone
We export Egyptian natural stone and granite. (blocks,slabs and Tiles)
We can deliver ANY type of Egyptian granite & natural stone.
(Galala, Triesta, Sunny, etc) with all finishings (Honed, Brushed, Polished, etc)
You name it, we deliver it fast! With the best packing methods, for a better price!

Thank you for your time.
Sincerely, on behalf of Egystone.

Roy Ahmed.
